Hello Nigel,

Thank you for getting back to us.

The machine will probably do not know how to comunicate with the EPP server since the IP was changed. 

For Clients installed on Windows-OS please see the tool below to change the IP addresses on the client side without needing to uninstall and reinstall them:
http://download.endpointprotector.com/Support_files/ClientIPChange.zip
Regarding the change ip for MacOS, can you please try the one below listed with the following steps from a terminal:
https://download.endpointprotector.com/Support_files/change_ip.zip
sudo chmod a+x /the path for the script/change_ip
sudo /the path for the script/change_ip IP_ADDRESS

Looking forward for your response.

Best regards,
